<h1 class="text-h2 md:text-h1 text-gray-1000 mb-0px">Best Stocks To Invest In: May 2023</h1>
<h2 class="mt-16px leading-relative-2">Here are 10 stocks that could be excellent additions to your portfolio for the rest of 2023 and for years to come.</h2>
<div class="font-medium text-gray-800 text-md md:text-lg mb-16px mt-20px md:my-24px">
By
<a class="text-cyan-800 hover:text-cyan-600 hover:underline" href="https://www.fool.com/author/2280/">Matthew Frankel, CFP</a> –
Updated
May 2, 2023 at 12:15PM
</div>
</div>
